Enum BlockSize

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<BlockSize>
      • com.github.unix_junkie.javafs.BlockSize
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Comparable<BlockSize>

    public enum BlockSize
extends Enum<BlockSize>

    BlockSize contains possible block sized this file system driver supports.

    Author:
    Andrew ``Bass'' Shcheglov <mailto:andrewbass@gmail.com>
